1.0.4.name: wordpress/openquote
1.0.4.description:
WordPress OpenQuote Component

Support Links Plugin Home and Demo Site Support Forum

Providing WordPress Integrated Insurance Quotations

Welcome to the OpenQuote plugin for WordPress. Created by Applied Industrial Logic, this component allows you to integrate OpenQuote insurance product quotations into any Wordpress 3 website. This plugin is licenced under the same GPL terms and conditions as the OpenQuote software.

OpenQuote

OpenQuote is an open source system, created by Applied Industrial Logic to help reduce both the time-to-market and costs of web-enabling quotations for insurance products and schemes. The software allows insurers, brokers and agents to efficiently release and maintain their products by configuring risk capture, risk
